snippet.title: I Was Lost - Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist it now! bit.ly/IWL-Steam
Move walls in a labyrinthic poem on this unique puzzle experience where each level is a poem's verse unraveling as you progress. ‏Control not only your position but also the walls to create new paths and escape from impossible situations
